		<span id="title-177025375" class="story-title"> <a   href="//news.slashdot.org/story/25/04/15/0144259/china-halts-rare-earth-exports-globally">China Halts Rare Earth Exports Globally</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://fortune.com/2025/04/14/china-rare-earth-exports-halt-trump-trade-war-tariff-retaliation/"  title="External link - https://fortune.com/2025/04/14/china-rare-earth-exports-halt-trump-trade-war-tariff-retaliation/" target="_blank"> (fortune.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
